{"tid":1626644,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"啲警方呼籲有冇得block咗佢","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:46:05.000Z","uid":63154,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"35d7c3a78549aa3c428de066d4db965431dc7bff","tid":1626644,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"好煩呀，唔想收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27f3f1c73e54467a168f11c96e9d5a15c864113","tid":1626644,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"8527d927c7fcabf54f3f73fd8cdfad10783ec2b4","tid":1626644,"uid":119524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"1835 000"},{"pid":"d61899fbfff5cf5a1f44be4f3f327e723236b9fd","tid":1626644,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fae4440d1f209cfc1e78e34679a1d6a54888e2","tid":1626644,"uid":1089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"